You didn't provoke them.

502
00:29:57,670 --> 00:29:59,547
You just did your job.

503
00:30:10,558 --> 00:30:11,476
The prosecution…

504
00:30:14,562 --> 00:30:16,606
will indict Hyun-woo tomorrow morning.

505
00:30:17,732 --> 00:30:20,819
They'll stop if you tell them
you're withdrawing before then.

506
00:30:25,615 --> 00:30:26,741
And if I don't?

507
00:30:29,828 --> 00:30:31,746
They'll keep backing us into a corner.

508
00:30:35,124 --> 00:30:36,251
Until Hyun-woo's life…

509
00:30:38,336 --> 00:30:40,046
can never return to normal.

510
00:30:50,557 --> 00:30:51,641
Ms. Oh!

511
00:30:56,062 --> 00:30:58,231
They've finished interrogating Hyun-woo.

512
00:31:34,601 --> 00:31:35,435
Kang Hyun-woo.

513
00:31:37,520 --> 00:31:38,354
Look at me.

514
00:31:39,856 --> 00:31:41,983
Are you not going to look at me? Huh?

515
00:31:42,567 --> 00:31:44,277
Will you never look at me again?

516
00:31:45,653 --> 00:31:47,655
Come over here. Now.

517
00:32:06,215 --> 00:32:07,592
Whatever the reason was…

518
00:32:10,553 --> 00:32:13,389
it's wrong to hit people.
You know that, don't you?

519
00:32:14,307 --> 00:32:16,225
That's what you're being punished for.

520
00:32:18,186 --> 00:32:19,479
But if it had been me

521
00:32:20,271 --> 00:32:24,317
seeing such an obscene photo
attached to my mom's face, mocking her,

522
00:32:24,859 --> 00:32:26,194
I would've lost my cool.

523
00:32:26,986 --> 00:32:28,863
How could I not? I would've hit him too.

524
00:32:39,290 --> 00:32:41,042
This is all my fault. I'm sorry.

525
00:32:42,293 --> 00:32:45,171
You're going through so much
all because of me.

526
00:32:47,423 --> 00:32:49,050
Why do you keep saying that?

527
00:32:51,803 --> 00:32:52,637
Listen.

528
00:32:55,098 --> 00:32:58,351
The other grown-ups
that are competing against me

529
00:32:59,352 --> 00:33:02,689
used your friends to provoke you
and put you here

530
00:33:04,065 --> 00:33:06,025
so that they could win the election.

531
00:33:10,363 --> 00:33:12,782
Grown-ups live
in such a cruel world, don't they?

532
00:33:13,783 --> 00:33:16,786
Those grown-ups upset me so much

533
00:33:17,412 --> 00:33:19,163
that I've been holding on until now

534
00:33:20,206 --> 00:33:21,416
to teach them a lesson.

535
00:33:26,045 --> 00:33:27,380
But I'm going to stop now.

536
00:33:33,386 --> 00:33:34,220
You see.

537
00:33:35,805 --> 00:33:37,432
I'm going to withdraw my candidacy.

538
00:33:39,183 --> 00:33:40,768
After putting you through this,

539
00:33:41,436 --> 00:33:43,646
being mayor of Seoul and all that…

540
00:33:45,023 --> 00:33:47,025
I'm not interested anymore. I won't do it.

541
00:33:47,108 --> 00:33:47,942
After all this?

542
00:33:51,320 --> 00:33:53,072
It's fine, okay?

543
00:33:55,950 --> 00:33:57,326
I know it's a bit too late,

544
00:33:57,410 --> 00:33:59,829
but I'm going to try
and be a proper mother. What?

545
00:33:59,912 --> 00:34:01,205
You don't think I can?

546
00:34:03,291 --> 00:34:04,125
I…

547
00:34:05,418 --> 00:34:07,295
I was the one who gave birth to you.

548
00:34:08,337 --> 00:34:10,256
I should be making sacrifices for you.

549
00:34:11,257 --> 00:34:14,927
How could I let you sacrifice yourself
for me instead? That just isn't right.

550
00:34:15,720 --> 00:34:17,138
I'm not sacrificing myself.

551
00:34:18,473 --> 00:34:20,099
All you have to do is win.

552
00:34:23,102 --> 00:34:24,270
If you give up…

553
00:34:26,856 --> 00:34:28,858
they'll keep making scapegoats like me.

554
00:34:30,401 --> 00:34:32,945
You have to win to teach them a lesson
and bring change.

555
00:34:34,072 --> 00:34:35,948
-Hyun-woo.
-I'm Oh Kyung-sook's son.

556
00:34:37,241 --> 00:34:39,160
While in your womb, I saw you protest.

557
00:34:39,744 --> 00:34:41,996
I've seen you fight for labor rights
for 15 years.

558
00:34:43,206 --> 00:34:44,582
I'm a mini rhino.

559
00:34:48,002 --> 00:34:50,505
Do you think I'll flinch
being locked up in here?

560
00:34:51,798 --> 00:34:54,217
I know that you'll win in the end
and get me out.

561
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:58,387
Hyun-woo, I'm not as great as
you think I am. Okay?

562
00:34:58,471 --> 00:35:00,181
I might not even win the election--

563
00:35:00,264 --> 00:35:01,474
You promised me.

564
00:35:02,517 --> 00:35:04,811
That you'd create a better world for me.

565
00:35:06,270 --> 00:35:08,981
That promise kept Dad and me going
for all this time.

566
00:35:10,566 --> 00:35:12,151
Are you going to let us down?

567
00:35:13,486 --> 00:35:16,197
Will you let me live in a world
built by those evil people?

568
00:35:19,534 --> 00:35:20,451
Hyun-woo.

569
00:35:22,120 --> 00:35:22,995
Jeez.

570
00:35:25,832 --> 00:35:27,416
I really wasn't going to cry.

571
00:35:28,668 --> 00:35:31,796
Why did you have to make me cry, huh?

572
00:35:33,381 --> 00:35:35,133
I'm sorry, honey.

573
00:35:38,719 --> 00:35:39,554
I'm sorry.

574
00:36:03,995 --> 00:36:04,829
Fine.

575
00:36:07,540 --> 00:36:08,374
Let's do this.

576
00:36:10,626 --> 00:36:12,086
We'll do this your way.

577
00:36:14,005 --> 00:36:15,339
We'll keep going.

578
00:36:19,343 --> 00:36:20,344
From now on,

579
00:36:22,180 --> 00:36:23,890
we'll do whatever it takes.

580
00:36:26,809 --> 00:36:28,477
Let's keep fighting to the end

581
00:36:30,229 --> 00:36:31,230
and win.

582
00:37:10,269 --> 00:37:15,942
FOR THE 39TH SEOUL CITY
MAYORAL BY-ELECTION D-7

583
00:37:39,215 --> 00:37:40,549
We have this game

584
00:37:41,050 --> 00:37:43,219
completely in our pocket now. Have a seat.

585
00:37:45,054 --> 00:37:47,390
How did we do in the most recent poll?

586
00:37:47,473 --> 00:37:50,351
We dominated the polls at 55%.

587
00:37:50,434 --> 00:37:51,435
Okay.

588
00:37:52,645 --> 00:37:55,231
Keep flooding the press
with that final poll.

589
00:37:56,274 --> 00:37:57,566
For the next week,

590
00:37:58,192 --> 00:38:00,569
we'll keep our rating at 55%.

591
00:38:01,529 --> 00:38:03,239
The swing voters always end up

592
00:38:03,823 --> 00:38:07,493
giving their votes to the candidate
who seems most likely to win.

593
00:38:07,576 --> 00:38:08,661
Yes, sir.

594
00:38:09,620 --> 00:38:10,454
But

595
00:38:11,622 --> 00:38:13,582
what should we do about Oh Kyung-sook?

596
00:38:14,166 --> 00:38:15,126
Just leave her.

597
00:38:15,209 --> 00:38:19,422
Whether she withdraws or not,
it's over for Oh Kyung-sook.

598
00:38:20,881 --> 00:38:21,716
Let's see.

599
00:38:22,925 --> 00:38:27,847
If Chairwoman Son would kindly share some
of her gold with the starving subjects,

600
00:38:28,514 --> 00:38:31,892
this election
would be wrapped up nicely, right?

601
00:38:32,560 --> 00:38:33,519
Good job, everyone.

602
00:38:43,571 --> 00:38:44,697
Of course.

603
00:38:46,157 --> 00:38:49,827
It's my turn to support Jae-min
when he's doing so well.

604
00:38:51,537 --> 00:38:53,205
And the duty-free shop's opening?

605
00:38:54,290 --> 00:38:55,916
Everything's perfectly prepared.

606
00:38:56,459 --> 00:39:00,046
I used my connections to invite
Korean and international celebrities.

607
00:39:00,129 --> 00:39:03,632
We'll also have all the media outlets
that owe us announce the opening,

608
00:39:03,716 --> 00:39:07,511
and I will give a speech at the end
as the CEO of the duty-free shop.

609
00:39:08,012 --> 00:39:08,846
Sound good?

610
00:39:08,929 --> 00:39:10,890
Focus the event on Jae-min.

611
00:39:11,766 --> 00:39:13,809
Don't try to hog all the spotlight.

612
00:39:15,686 --> 00:39:18,981
Starting tomorrow,
have the duty-free shop open 24 hours

613
00:39:19,065 --> 00:39:20,983
until the day of the election.

614
00:39:21,650 --> 00:39:25,321
Leave it open so that anyone can shop
as long as they're Seoul citizens.

615
00:39:25,404 --> 00:39:26,989
-Mom.
-Ma'am.

616
00:39:27,823 --> 00:39:31,369
I know that you're feeling generous,
but that's a bit--

617
00:39:31,452 --> 00:39:34,455
And the duty-free shop's official opening
will be held

618
00:39:34,538 --> 00:39:36,624
on the day Jae-min wins the election.

619
00:39:44,006 --> 00:39:45,549
What are you doing here?

620
00:39:49,512 --> 00:39:50,346
What's wrong?

621
00:39:51,430 --> 00:39:52,723
Am I not welcome here?

622
00:39:53,724 --> 00:39:55,309
I may have left my position,

623
00:39:55,393 --> 00:39:58,145
but I'm still a key member
of the Eunsung Group board.

624
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:02,817
Our chairwoman's lifelong dream,
Eunsung Duty-Free Shop,

625
00:40:03,692 --> 00:40:05,861
will hold its soft opening event tomorrow.

626
00:40:06,737 --> 00:40:08,948
I should be kept in the loop.

627
00:40:10,699 --> 00:40:12,618
Especially with the election imminent.

628
00:40:15,454 --> 00:40:16,288
What's wrong?

629
00:40:18,916 --> 00:40:21,419
It's only when my husband is elected

630
00:40:22,044 --> 00:40:24,797
that the duty-free shop
can officially open, isn't it?

631
00:40:26,507 --> 00:40:29,468
You need him to cover up
everything illegal we did,

632
00:40:29,552 --> 00:40:32,513
from getting site permits
to passing the building inspection.

633
00:40:33,097 --> 00:40:36,642
He also needs to use his power
as mayor to exempt us

634
00:40:37,143 --> 00:40:40,938
from the final safety inspection
so we can decide

635
00:40:41,564 --> 00:40:43,190
whether to open the shop or not.

636
00:40:43,774 --> 00:40:44,775
Have you lost it?

637
00:40:46,152 --> 00:40:47,570
What are you trying to say?

638
00:40:52,366 --> 00:40:54,452
We shouldn't underestimate Oh Kyung-sook.

639
00:40:56,829 --> 00:41:01,125
She won't give in even when we try
burying her son alive to make her quit.

640
00:41:02,626 --> 00:41:05,129
If she were to discover
that the duty-free shop

641
00:41:05,212 --> 00:41:07,798
is a hunk of metal
built on all sorts of corruption,

642
00:41:08,424 --> 00:41:10,259
the tables might turn.

643
00:41:11,677 --> 00:41:13,971
If Oh Kyung-sook ends up becoming mayor,

644
00:41:14,847 --> 00:41:17,349
what will happen to us, Chairwoman Son?

645
00:41:17,433 --> 00:41:18,267
Wait.

646
00:41:20,311 --> 00:41:23,981
Maybe I should ask the future CEO
of Eunsung Duty-Free Shop.

647
00:41:28,402 --> 00:41:32,531
If your figurehead can't even come up
with a solution in an emergency like this,

648
00:41:33,407 --> 00:41:36,744
would she really be able
to do her job as the CEO?

649
00:41:39,788 --> 00:41:42,374
I'd like to hear
what the chairwoman thinks.

650
00:41:44,877 --> 00:41:50,049
I think it's time we talked privately,
Director Eun.

651
00:42:08,150 --> 00:42:10,027
My youngest has come a long way.

652
00:42:12,154 --> 00:42:15,241
You even know
how to threaten your mother now.

653
00:42:15,991 --> 00:42:17,368
It's always been like this.

654
00:42:20,579 --> 00:42:24,041
I couldn't get your attention
unless I pulled a crazy stunt like this.

655
00:42:30,506 --> 00:42:34,635
Were you worried I was going to give
your sister the duty-free shop?

656
00:42:37,346 --> 00:42:38,514
More like offended.

657
00:42:40,641 --> 00:42:44,144
I've even put up with Baek Jae-min
sowing his wild oats everywhere

658
00:42:44,228 --> 00:42:45,563
to get where I am.

659
00:42:49,775 --> 00:42:51,110
He's something, isn't he?

660
00:42:53,070 --> 00:42:55,489
Making an illegitimate child
at a time like this.

661
00:43:05,916 --> 00:43:10,212
We can always dig out the seed
that is sown outside of my walls.

662
00:43:10,296 --> 00:43:12,298
I'll deal with that problem, so--

663
00:43:12,381 --> 00:43:13,215
You know what?

664
00:43:14,133 --> 00:43:15,801
I'll raise that child as my own.

665
00:43:24,476 --> 00:43:26,478
Just like how you took me in,

666
00:43:27,896 --> 00:43:29,607
Father's illegitimate child.

667
00:43:33,110 --> 00:43:34,028
Chae-ryoung!

668
00:43:34,111 --> 00:43:37,281
He'll have to announce it
as he's in line for public office.

669
00:43:39,450 --> 00:43:43,203
I'll have him come clean to everyone
that he has an illegitimate child…

670
00:43:45,831 --> 00:43:47,583
and make him give up the election.

671
00:43:48,208 --> 00:43:49,043
You…

672
00:43:50,336 --> 00:43:53,422
Are you trying
to hang your mother out to dry?

673
00:43:53,505 --> 00:43:55,674
Would any daughter want to do that?

674
00:43:56,967 --> 00:43:58,344
I lived my entire life…

675
00:44:00,387 --> 00:44:02,598
doing my best to become your daughter.

676
00:44:03,223 --> 00:44:06,644
I wanted people to tell me
that I took after you more than Seo-jin,

677
00:44:06,727 --> 00:44:08,395
the daughter you gave birth to.

678
00:44:08,479 --> 00:44:10,981
So I tried hard
to learn how to run this company.

679
00:44:12,316 --> 00:44:14,610
Even if I didn't inherit your blood,

680
00:44:16,320 --> 00:44:19,073
I held on so far, thinking
I'd become your real daughter

681
00:44:19,156 --> 00:44:20,699
if I inherited the company.

682
00:44:21,325 --> 00:44:24,119
So give me the same chance
you gave Seo-jin.

683
00:44:26,080 --> 00:44:28,374
The chance to become
Eunsung Group's owner.

684
00:44:30,751 --> 00:44:34,213
If you promise me that,
I'll focus on this election as you want.

685
00:44:37,966 --> 00:44:39,301
I'll do whatever it takes…

686
00:44:42,554 --> 00:44:44,181
to make that bastard mayor.

687
00:45:05,077 --> 00:45:05,911
All right.

688
00:45:09,540 --> 00:45:11,125
I'll do what you want me to do.

689
00:45:14,002 --> 00:45:14,837
My daughter.

690
00:45:40,195 --> 00:45:41,530
How did it go?

691
00:45:41,613 --> 00:45:45,659
Ms. Eun Chae-ryoung will attend
the duty-free shop's soft opening

692
00:45:46,243 --> 00:45:47,453
with her husband.

693
00:45:49,496 --> 00:45:50,748
And the CEO position?

694
00:45:50,831 --> 00:45:54,460
It seems that Chairwoman Son will give it
to Director Eun Chae-ryoung.

695
00:46:04,094 --> 00:46:07,639
HWANG DO-HEE

696
00:46:33,415 --> 00:46:35,000
You seem better than I thought.

697
00:46:35,793 --> 00:46:38,086
You sounded desperate,
so I thought you'd be dying.

698
00:46:38,921 --> 00:46:41,048
What for? I have no reason to be.

699
00:46:44,510 --> 00:46:46,011
My heart flutters even more.

700
00:46:47,095 --> 00:46:49,056
Why would the high and mighty Ms. Hwang

701
00:46:49,807 --> 00:46:53,769
ask to see a nobody like me
when she isn't in any imminent danger?

702
00:46:57,022 --> 00:46:58,482
The offer you made me before.

703
00:47:00,275 --> 00:47:01,527
Is that still on?

704
00:47:04,488 --> 00:47:05,447
The 20 billion won.

705
00:47:07,074 --> 00:47:08,951
Can you get it in cash by tomorrow?

706
00:47:13,956 --> 00:47:15,958
How the mighty have fallen.

707
00:47:18,001 --> 00:47:21,171
You wouldn't take an umbrella from us
even if it were pouring,

708
00:47:21,672 --> 00:47:24,341
but now that Oh Kyung-sook
might end up losing,

709
00:47:24,424 --> 00:47:26,760
you're crawling back to us for help?

710
00:47:26,844 --> 00:47:28,846
How humiliating.

711
00:47:31,932 --> 00:47:34,309
This is too good to just watch on my own.

712
00:47:36,603 --> 00:47:38,188
Ms. Hwang, of all people,

713
00:47:39,189 --> 00:47:42,234
is begging me for money!

714
00:47:44,903 --> 00:47:47,823
This stupidity is
why you always lost to Chae-ryoung.

715
00:47:49,116 --> 00:47:53,328
Private life, marriage,
and corporate management skills.

716
00:47:53,412 --> 00:47:55,497
Are you better than Chae-ryoung
at anything?

717
00:47:58,041 --> 00:47:59,877
You don't want to lose your mom's favor,

718
00:47:59,960 --> 00:48:02,087
but you know you are
no match for Chae-ryoung,

719
00:48:02,170 --> 00:48:04,965
so you keep running away,
pretending to be tough and cool,

720
00:48:05,048 --> 00:48:07,175
trying to hide your inferiority complex.

721
00:48:09,386 --> 00:48:10,220
Shut your mouth.

722
00:48:11,388 --> 00:48:13,765
The only advantage you have
over Chae-ryoung

723
00:48:13,849 --> 00:48:16,351
is that you were born
to the chairwoman legitimately.

724
00:48:16,435 --> 00:48:18,478
I told you to shut your mouth!

725
00:48:19,062 --> 00:48:20,480
Don't you throw a fit at me.

726
00:48:21,648 --> 00:48:24,276
I'm giving you the chance
of a lifetime now.

727
00:48:31,283 --> 00:48:32,326
I'm going to win…

728
00:48:34,870 --> 00:48:36,663
this election, whatever it takes.

729
00:48:40,375 --> 00:48:41,668
Then Baek Jae-min

730
00:48:43,086 --> 00:48:45,339
will be discarded by your mother.

731
00:48:45,422 --> 00:48:47,799
Chae-ryoung will fall out of favor
with him too.

732
00:48:49,509 --> 00:48:51,053
And meanwhile, you will end up

733
00:48:51,595 --> 00:48:55,599
with a direct connection
to Mayor Oh Kyung-sook's office.

734
00:48:55,682 --> 00:48:56,516
Then…

735
00:48:59,144 --> 00:49:01,063
you will be the one holding hegemony

736
00:49:01,939 --> 00:49:02,898
in Eunsung Group.

737
00:49:07,778 --> 00:49:09,071
You think you can win?

738
00:49:11,073 --> 00:49:13,075
When things are this hopeless?

739
00:49:23,961 --> 00:49:25,212
Have you forgotten already?

740
00:49:27,422 --> 00:49:29,424
I've never lost, not even once.

741
00:49:30,759 --> 00:49:31,969
Yes. I'm well aware.

742
00:49:34,471 --> 00:49:36,139
So let's say I inherit Eunsung,

743
00:49:37,349 --> 00:49:40,394
and Oh Kyung-sook becomes mayor,
as you said.

744
00:49:42,229 --> 00:49:43,313
What about you?

745
00:49:45,607 --> 00:49:46,942
What do you get out of it?

746
00:49:58,870 --> 00:50:00,122
Have it ready by tomorrow.

747
00:51:59,825 --> 00:52:01,076
Have some of this.

748
00:52:04,579 --> 00:52:07,165
You little brat.
I told you to stop playing video games.

749
00:52:07,249 --> 00:52:09,209
Just leave me alone.

750
00:52:20,554 --> 00:52:21,805
How dare you come here?

751
00:52:23,723 --> 00:52:26,226
I wanted to see
if Gyeong-min was recovering well.

752
00:52:27,018 --> 00:52:29,354
There was also something
I wanted to ask him.

753
00:52:31,231 --> 00:52:33,984
If you have any questions,
go ask the prosecutors.

754
00:52:34,067 --> 00:52:35,986
We have nothing to say to you.

